    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with qualitative justification. NIH predictions agree with bench data within combined uncertainty at all validation points. The model is accepted for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as described in the claim and requirement documentation.",
